Return Public PTAB Proceedings InformationReturn PTAB Proceedings Information for given search input. Here are some examples of input format:
 E.g. 1. 
 {<br>  "facetMap": {"prosecutionStatus": ["FWD Entered"]},<br>  "paramMap": {},<br>  "rows": 0,<br>  "sortByColumn": "string",<br>  "sortOrder": "string",<br>  "start": 0<br>}
 E.g. 2. 
{<br>  "facetMap": {"petitionerName": ["Liberty Mutual Insurance Company", "SAP America, Inc."]},<br>  "paramMap": {"proceedingNumber":"CBM2012-00001", "patentNumber":"6553350"},<br>  "rows": 20,<br>  "sortByColumn": "patentNumber",<br>  "sortOrder": "desc",<br>  "start": 0<br>}
 E.g. 3. {}
 <em><strong>Please DO NOT copy/paste, rather type in.</strong></em> For more filter values, refer to the response of above GET (/trials) end point for the trials

Returns PTAB Public Documents for given search input. Here are some examples of input format:

 E.g. 1.
{<br>  "facetMap": {"filingParty": ["board"]},<br>  "paramMap": {},<br>  "rows": 10,<br>  "start": 2<br>}

 E.g. 2. 
{<br>  "facetMap": {"filingParty": ["board", "petitioner"], "type": ["notice"]},<br>  "paramMap": {"documentNumber":"73", "title":"power of attorney"},<br>  "rows": 20,<br>  "sortByColumn": "type",<br>  "sortOrder": "desc",<br>  "start": 0<br>}

 E.g. 3. {}

 E.g. 4. 
{<br>"dateRangeMap": {"filingDatetime": {"start": "2014-03-12", "end": "2014-03-15"}},<br>  "sortMapArray": [<br>    {"type":"asc"}, {"title":"desc"}<br>  ],<br>  "rows": 15,<br>  "start": 6<br>}

 <em><strong>Please DO NOT copy/paste, rather type in to avoid ascii chars issue or something else.</strong></em>

For more filter/param values for Documents, refer to the response of above GET (/documents) end point.
